  {
    "id": "E54_03",
    "change_type": "added",
    "content": "## コミットメッセージ形式\n\nコミットメッセージは以下の形式に従ってください：\n\n```\n<type>(<scope>): <subject>\n\n<body>\n\n<footer>\n```",
    "project": "web-roulette-app",
    "file": "commit-rules.mdc.diff",
    "commit_id": "4a6f177f1e2f5e335979a50f7233940dce3f2142",
    "first_level": "Development Workflow & Project Management",
    "second_level": "Version Control",
    "constraint_degree": "Mandatory"
  },
  {
    "id": "E54_04",
    "change_type": "added",
    "content": "### Type\n\n- **feat**: 新機能\n- **fix**: バグ修正\n- **docs**: ドキュメント関連\n- **style**: コードスタイルの変更（インデント，セミコロン等）\n- **refactor**: リファクタリング\n- **test**: テスト関連\n- **chore**: ビルドプロセスやツール，ライブラリ更新など",
    "project": "web-roulette-app",
    "file": "commit-rules.mdc.diff",
    "commit_id": "4a6f177f1e2f5e335979a50f7233940dce3f2142",
    "first_level": "Development Workflow & Project Management",
    "second_level": "Version Control",
    "constraint_degree": "Mandatory"
  },
  {
    "id": "E54_05",
    "change_type": "added",
    "content": "### Scope（任意）\n\n変更の範囲を示します（例：ui，api，auth など）",
    "project": "web-roulette-app",
    "file": "commit-rules.mdc.diff",
    "commit_id": "4a6f177f1e2f5e335979a50f7233940dce3f2142",
    "first_level": "Development Workflow & Project Management",
    "second_level": "Version Control",
    "constraint_degree": "Optional"
  },
  {
    "id": "E54_06",
    "change_type": "added",
    "content": "### Subject\n\n変更内容を簡潔に表現します（命令形で記述）：\n- 最大50文字以内\n- 先頭は小文字\n- 末尾にピリオドなし",
    "project": "web-roulette-app",
    "file": "commit-rules.mdc.diff",
    "commit_id": "4a6f177f1e2f5e335979a50f7233940dce3f2142",
    "first_level": "Development Workflow & Project Management",
    "second_level": "Version Control",
    "constraint_degree": "Mandatory"
  },
  {
    "id": "E54_07",
    "change_type": "added",
    "content": "### Body（任意）\n\n変更の詳細と理由を記述します：\n- 何が変わったか\n- なぜその変更が必要だったか\n- 72文字で改行",
    "project": "web-roulette-app",
    "file": "commit-rules.mdc.diff",
    "commit_id": "4a6f177f1e2f5e335979a50f7233940dce3f2142",
    "first_level": "Development Workflow & Project Management",
    "second_level": "Version Control",
    "constraint_degree": "Optional"
  },
  {
    "id": "E54_08",
    "change_type": "added",
    "content": "### Footer（任意）\n\n- Breaking Changes\n- 関連Issue（例：`Fixes #123`，`Closes #456`）",
    "project": "web-roulette-app",
    "file": "commit-rules.mdc.diff",
    "commit_id": "4a6f177f1e2f5e335979a50f7233940dce3f2142",
    "first_level": "Development Workflow & Project Management",
